name: PEPECASTRO - Series 2, Card 27 Rarepepe - John Villar Created 46 issued, 19 lost forever, 27 in existence
description:
PEPECASTRO is a Series 2, Card 27 Rarepepe that was created by the legend John Villar(RIP) with 46 issued. There are only 27 PEPECASTROs that remain in existence due to the 19 that are lost forever in 4 absolutely dead/lost addresses. The largest holder is John Villar's RarePepeParty Game Address, which holds 15 and is very well known and documented that the keys to that address were lost forever. The other 3 addresses that hold the other 4 lost PEPECASTROs, have been non-existent for 5+ years. 

This RarePepe is a truly Dank piece of Art & History.
